4 SENATE BILL 489
1 (ii) The applicant successfully completed a fifth pathway program
2 and submits evidence acceptable to the Board that the applicant:
3 1. Has a document issued by the international medical school
4 certifying that the applicant completed all of the formal requirements of that school for the
5 study of medicine, except for the postgraduate or social service components as required by
